    correct_answer: { ids: ['a', 'b', 'c', 'e'] },
    rationale: 'CLABSI bundle: hand hygiene, maximal sterile barrier precautions, chlorhexidine (CHG) skin antisepsis, optimal site selection, daily review of line necessity. Standard IV tubing is changed every 72–96 hours (not 24h). Lipid tubing changes every 24 hours.',
