    correct_answer: { ids: ['a', 'b', 'c', 'd', 'e'] },
    rationale: 'All five increase fall risk: benzodiazepines (sedation), beta-blockers (bradycardia, orthostatic hypotension), ACE inhibitors (orthostatic hypotension), diphenhydramine (anticholinergic confusion/sedation — Beers Criteria), and opioids (sedation, dizziness). High-risk fall precautions warranted.',
